{"tid":2082420,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[估歌仔] 有無人知\"頂！磁力共振九龍城\"係咩歌","createTime":"2020-06-28T04:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:45:08.000Z","uid":44331,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b19eed62738c7c639c5dafa593fc8ff8c523c5","tid":2082420,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"歌詞係咁（好似係）：<br />\n頂　磁力共振九龍城<br />\n頂　毛遂自薦當年情<br />\n我　死去活來易　打飛機更易<br />\n歇斯底里　循序漸進<br />\n<br />\n之後副歌係：<br />\n廉政公署 廉政公署<br />\n刑事毀壞 刑事毀壞<br />\n危在旦夕 危在旦夕<br />\n牛記笠記 牛記笠記<br />\n唔制得過 唔制得過<br />\n名譽掃地 名譽掃地<br />\n人道毀滅 人道毀滅<br />\n來電顯示 來電顯示<br />\n<br />\n頂！磁力共振九龍城！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提示：其實係用呢個數字填詞生成器９ＧＥＮ出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://wordshk.github.io/yue_references/1234%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E5%99%A8/1234.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwordshk.github.io%2Fyue_references%2F1234%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A9%259E%25E5%2599%25A8%2F1234.html&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7bfeb905\" target=\"_blank\">https://wordshk.github.io/yue_references/1234%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E5%99%A8/1234.html</a><br />\n<br />\n利用呢舊９野，你地用係其他歌，又會有咩新創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9075af8e7622bb0a3aa2a83565801893d6951de3","tid":2082420,"uid":35301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"文字生成器後 有填詞生成器..."},{"pid":"47627a5fcf6d6