4331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:57:31.000Z","msg":"我好粗咁用個生成器將&quot;我射了進去&quot;改左做廣東話<br />\n拋磚引玉：<br />\n<br />\n大會堂十字路口往陣時<br />\n轉眼間一拍兩散似是而非<br />\n洋紫荊詩情畫意到痺<br />\n失戀傷心到死<br />\n喜慶事未有佳期<br />\n  <br />\n刻骨銘心 認命不太易<br />\n報應睇得化 放棄發花痴<br />\n無期睇開啲 Ａ０拍拖貪得意<br />\n運滯無法子 搭錯線不可思議<br />\n  <br />\n唔駛問亞貴 樣衰確係曳<br />\n桃花運煞掣 咩玩法就黎自閉<br />\n談戀愛黑仔 萬劫不復兵仔橫空出世<br />\n笨實無得救 無定性正仆街仔"},{"pid":"0760d8498d189637eb433b56942bd70ea7009cf9","tid":2082420,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb6711da07b8d932ea5a573376b1df3fa866a71","tid":2082420,"uid":200944,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:47:12.000Z","msg":"林子祥 數字人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:57:36.000Z","msg":"你估得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e072e1e4c1ad46f9fa6f9fcafed29998c36c15a2","tid":2082420,"uid":44331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab6439e0f665a737954dd22f8c3ee9974c6bba13","tid":2082420,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"假使可以 五區當選<br />\n錦滿會打交 松泰負責投下反對票<br />\n這樣議事很足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有你個github 呢啲教會歌咪會絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p